    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318170/extras/7b4854fc1fc1866e4eeff1b1ab581285.avif?t=1769526032\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a lowly <strong>lust demon</strong> dreaming of making the goddess <strong>Era</strong> yours in the future. One day, the <strong>bored and sadistic goddess</strong>, after hearing your dream, descends into your dungeon with a bet: <strong>survive and seduce her seven chosen warriors, and she will consider making your dreams a reality.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318170/extras/16098ece78b38bd183441a703854e7c3.avif?t=1769526032\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Idle Harem Dungeon</strong> is a relaxing <strong>idle</strong> game about defeating an endless number of adventurers flocking into your dungeon. Grow stronger through battle, meet <strong>eight beautiful girls, seduce them, and make them part of your dream harem.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318170/extras/9792919b4ea0f790fbd6da21b2d7836f.avif?t=1769526032\" width=1600 height=400 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eight lovely and unique girls</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful pixel art aesthetic</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cute and interesting dialogues</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Floating eyeballs with wings</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Numbers going up</strong></p></li></ul>",
